<br />
<br />Oh. If that's the only thing, use this javascript instead:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&lt;script&gt;<br />function writefsr&#40;&#41; &#123;<br />&nbsp; var i,N=1;<br /><br />&nbsp; do &#123; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; N=&#40;N&lt;&lt;1&#41;+&#40;&#40;N&gt;&gt;13&#41;&amp;1&#41;^&#40;&#40;N&gt;&gt;14&#41;&amp;1&#41;;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; N &amp;= 0x7FFF;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; document.write&#40;&#40;&#40;&#40;N&gt;&gt;14&#41;&amp;1&#41;?'z':'0'&#41;&#41;; <br />&nbsp; &#125; while &#40;N != 1&#41;;<br />&nbsp;&#125;<br />&lt;/script&gt;<br /><br />&lt;body onLoad=&quot;javascript:writefsr&#40;&#41;;&quot;&gt;<br />&lt;/body&gt;</div>
<br />
<br />Save it to an html file, load that in a web browser (i've only tested in firefox but i can't imagine IE wouldn't work), copy and paste the text to a new file, and import as raw audio.

		

